<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VineShade</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/olaffx/VineShade/main/icon.png">
    
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #1a1a24; 
            --bottle-red: #8b2d30; 
            --label-beige: #f5e0c3; 
        }

        body { 
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; 
            background-color: var(--bg-color); 
            color: white; 
        }

        .btn-premium {
            background-color: var(--bottle-red);
            transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        .btn-premium:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            filter: brightness(1.1);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px -5px rgba(139, 45, 48, 0.4);
        }

        .glass-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        .text-beige { color: var(--label-beige); }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="antialiased">

    <nav class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-8 flex justify-between items-center">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 font-extrabold text-xl tracking-tight">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/olaffx/VineShade/main/icon.png" alt="VineShade" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            VineShade
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-8">
            <a href="https://github.com/olaffx/VineShade" class="text-zinc-400 hover:text-white transition font-semibold text-sm">GitHub</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/olaffx/VineShade/releases/latest" class="btn-premium px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-sm">Download</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="pt-20 pb-32 px-6 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="mb-12 flex justify-center">
                <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/olaffx/VineShade/main/icon.png" 
                     alt="VineShade Logo" 
                     class="w-36 h-36 rounded-[2.2rem] shadow-2xl border-2 border-white/5 transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500">
            </div>

            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tighter leading-tight">
                Better graphics. <br> <span class="text-beige italic">No compromises.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 mb-12 max-w-xl mx-auto font-medium leading-relaxed">
                VineShade is a native Linux tool that seamlessly integrates high-end shaders into your Roblox experience.
            </p>

            <a href="https://github.com/olaffx/VineShade/releases/latest" 
               class="btn-premium px-12 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-bold inline-flex items-center gap-3 shadow-2xl">
                Get VineShade v2.0
            </a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 mb-40">
        <div class="glass-card rounded-[2.5rem] p-2 shadow-2xl">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/olaffx/VineShade/main/main.png" 
                 alt="Application Preview" 
                 class="rounded-[2rem] w-full h-auto max-h-[650px] object-contain block opacity-95">
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 mb-40 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 text-center">
        <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-beige">Native GUI</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">Built with Libadwaita for a seamless, modern Linux desktop experience.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-beige">Sober Ready</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">Automatically detects and hooks into the Sober Flatpak environment.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-beige">Ban Safe</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">Uses post-processing layers instead of DLL injection to keep your account safe.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-20 border-t border-white/5 text-center">
        <p class="text-zinc-600 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Developed by olaffx</p>
        <p class="text-zinc-800 text-[10px] max-w-xs mx-auto leading-tight">VineShade is an independent fan project and is not affiliated with Roblox Corp.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
